'''First West Coast''' is one of the shortlisted railway companies bidding for the [[InterCity West Coast Franchise]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www2.dft.gov.uk/pgr/rail/passenger/franchises/greater-anglia/franchisebidders.pdf | title=dft.gov.uk/ | accessdate=October 17, 2011}}</ref>. It's parent company is [[FirstGroup|First]].
==The Franchise== The government will announce the winning bidders in Autumn 2011. The franchise will start on the 1 April 2012 lasting for 14 years (March 2026) with an optional one year extension.
